rows.label: qst104221_msg0001
rows.name:
Oh, Toatoa is energetically
researching today as well, mo.

rows.label: qst104221_msg0002
rows.name:
Toatoa examines salvaged items, and if
they're old, Toatoa thinks about what they
were used for and why they were made...mo.

rows.label: qst104221_msg0003
rows.name:
Thinking about the history of
things makes Toatoa unable to
sleep, mo. It's romantic, mo.

rows.label: qst104221_msg0004
rows.name:
Toatoa has traveled to many countries
and salvaged things, but...

rows.label: qst104221_msg0005
rows.name:
Toatoa wants to meet someone
who will listen seriously
to this romance...mo...

rows.label: qst104221_msg0006
rows.name:
A teacher in Iyasaki Village?
Toatoa will be teaching, mo?

rows.label: qst104221_msg0007
qst104221_msg0008
rows.name:
...Wait a moment, mo! Before
becoming a teacher, there is
something Toatoa wants to obtain, mo.

rows.label: qst104221_msg0009
rows.name:
The Ancient Salvaging Suit... Toatoa
doesn't even know where to find it, mo.
If friends find it, Toatoa will go, mo.

rows.label: qst104221_msg0051
rows.name: Really invite Toatoa to be a teacher?

rows.label: qst104221_msg0052
rows.name: Invite

rows.label: qst104221_msg0053
rows.name: Think it over

rows.label: qst104221_msg0061
rows.name:
Will friends help, mo?
Toatoa is so happy, mo.

rows.label: qst104221_msg0062
rows.name:
Toatoa just needs one Ancient
Salvaging Suit, mo. Please
bring it here, mo.

rows.label: qst104221_msg0063
rows.name:
Toatoa doesn't know where
to get it, though...mo...

rows.label: qst104221_msg0081
rows.name:
Understood, mo. Toatoa will
search for the Ancient Salvaging
Suit on her own, mo.

rows.label: qst104221_msg0101
rows.name:
Do friends still want Toatoa
to be a teacher, mo?

rows.label: qst104221_msg0121
rows.name:
The Ancient Salvaging Suit...
Maybe it's in a place people
don't normally go, mo?

rows.label: qst104221_msg0122
rows.name:
Rex and friends might be salvaging
in some Cloud Sea somewhere...mo?

rows.label: qst104221_msg0123
rows.name:
There are so many unknowns,
mo. Patience is a virtue, mo.

rows.label: qst104221_msg0151
rows.name:
The Ancient Salvaging Suit!!
Th-This is... so big, mo!

rows.label: qst104221_msg0152
rows.name:
Wearing something like this
would make it hard to move and
difficult to salvage, mo.

rows.label: qst104221_msg0153
rows.name:
...But there must be a
reason for this size, mo!

rows.label: qst104221_msg0154
rows.name:
When Toatoa goes to Iyasaki Village,
Toatoa will research the history of
the Ancient Salvaging Suit, mo!

rows.label: qst104221_msg0155
rows.name:
And then, Toatoa will teach
a class on the side, mo!

rows.label: qst104221_msg0156
rows.name:
Well then, once Toatoa packs up
her salvaging tools, Toatoa will
go to Iyasaki Village, mo~

rows.label: qst104221_msg0201
rows.name:
Have friends found a teacher,
mo? That's good, mo.

rows.label: qst104221_msg0301
rows.name:
But it's rare to meet such
a person... Harder than
finding treasure, mo.
